# Create a free Redis database at https://upstash.com (Vercel Marketplace
# also offers "Upstash for Redis" directly from your Vercel project).
# Copy the REST URL and token it gives you into Vercel's Project Settings ->
# Environment Variables (do NOT commit real values to this file).

UPSTASH_REDIS_REST_URL=
UPSTASH_REDIS_REST_TOKEN=
